{"tid":2456993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂逝世悼念活動 區議員助理遭制服期間涉批踭襲警受審","createTime":"2021-03-22T10:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T12:22:39.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2453e5be238a4ccc9d8d855226efcf53fe916c","tid":2456993,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"科大學生周梓樂前年逝世兩個月當日，網民發起晚上到將軍澳尚德邨舉行悼念活動。警方當晚要求拿著圓藤盾的議員助理葉離開，葉反向警方謂：「咩呀！你揸武器就得！我揸武器就唔得？」及後葉被指向警員批踭遭拘控，今就襲警罪受審。辯方指被告當時遭警員踢，並被警方圓盾壓背，被告因此才意外接觸警員。案件表證成立，被告不作供，但會傳召一名品格證人。<br />\n<br />\n鄭同意將被告制服地下期間，曾有同袍施放胡椒噴劑，射中被告面部。他曾問被告有否受傷，但被告沒有回答。鄭其後帶被告返回警署，被告向值日官稱右眼角、右手腕、左手手背及小腿都有擦傷，並展示傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n鄭看完新聞直播影片後同意，見到有<span class=\"red\">警員向被告方向「抽動」兩下</span>。至於意外接觸一說，鄭不同意，更指被告批踭動作並非不自主，「我睇到呢一肘係有心，唔係你所講嘅接觸」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又在庭上播出兩段新聞直播影片，指影片沒有拍到被告推鄭，或者想爬、逃走的情況，更指被告表現冷靜。鄭同意影片拍不到他所供述的情況。至於被告冷靜與否，鄭解釋被告已被胡椒噴霧射中，完全失去行動能力，又強調<span class=\"red\">「喺我角度，佢手郁，我覺得係意圖想走，可能佢動作幅度細先影唔到」。</span>"},{"pid":"77790e37ce79759ea6c10ca2b23dc9c8190d5e52","tid":2456993,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"裁判官<span class=\"red\">莫子聰</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210322/R47H2VFDUJDFTDMA6IGIJHSM6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210322%2FR47H2VFDUJDFTDMA6IGIJHSM6Y%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=1d5f02b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210322%2FR47H2VFDUJDFTDMA6IGIJHSM6Y%2F&h=0576947c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210322/R47H2VFDUJDFTDMA6IGIJHSM6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"0d48cf8319dc00827f74042472742cdb8c002c6f","tid":2456993,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0863c1752419e8fb91eb9589c04c84ba0f406aa0","tid":2456993,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0414f1e421edb881923fe720e693b323230454db","tid":2456993,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52bda0cb6953644a6dd5c15f7d0f1e610d43eff","tid":2456993,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b981b9746f36badb11b50e1511803af4127177","tid":2456993,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c48d1a42d4f2141ad19d16ba0016d4df94fdfd","tid":2456993,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773241ed9029a1be19c163e677fecb3380301e95","tid":2456993,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec185842a09706f935530d2808e52f7115dfc766","tid":2456993,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"天滅中共，全黨死清光"},{"pid":"1cdd8438162fc254ef675eb6cf1bd9bbb18a5f6d","tid":2456993,"uid":92448,"li